sources.title: Double Duty | Full Action Movie | Tom Sizemore | Mimi Lesseos
sources.description:
Double Duty - Action-packed coming of age story portrays *Lesseos* as an ex-marine trying to adjust to civilian life and discover her feminine side, with help from best friend Sophia. Many obstacles are thrown in her path, resulting in edge of your seat action scenes. Her love interest, Craig is sweet and soft-spoken but is intrigued with M.J.'s tough side, creating a hilarious dynamic duo that keeps us laughing as well as touches our hearts.
2009. Stars: Mimi Lesseos, Tom Sizemore, Susan Duerden
